high_descs: Move to the desk on the right facing the alarm clock
Pick up the alarm clock that is sitting on top of the desk
Carry the alarm clock to the other desk to the left
Place the alarm clock on top of the CD that is closest to the book
anns.task_desc: Carry an alarm clock to place on top of a CD that is on top of a desk

high_descs: Turn to the left and take one step then turn to the right to face the desk.
Take the alarm clock next to the keys.
Turn to the right and walk across the room, then turn left.
Place the alarm clock on top of the CD that is next to the book.
anns.task_desc: To put the alarm clock on the desk.

high_descs: Take a step to your left so you're standing in front of the alarm clock.
Pick up the alarm clock please.
Take two steps to your right so you standing in front of a book with a phone to the left of it.
Put the alarm clock on the left CD.
anns.task_desc: Put an alarm clock on the desk.
